Class KeyStrokes

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jmeter.gui.action.KeyStrokes
  • public final class KeyStrokes
extends java.lang.Object
    Collect all the keystrokes together in one place. This helps to ensure that there are no duplicates.
